{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"update"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this method to update the appearance of the user location annotation. This"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method is called by the associated map view when it has determined that the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"user location annotation needs to be updated. This can happen in response to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"user interaction, a change in the user’s location, when the user tracking mode"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"changes, or when the viewport changes."}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"During user interaction with the map, this method may be called many","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"times to update the user location annotation. Therefore, your implementation of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this method should be as lightweight as possible to avoid negatively affecting","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"performance.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Note","style":"note"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView\/update"},"sections":[],"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"update"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView.h#L59","fileName":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView.h"},"fragments":[{"kind"